snippet.title: EmergeNYC - Welcome to Montgomery County
snippet.description:
Welcome to Montgomery County, a small rural area located in Upstate New York. Run a volunteer Fire Department, a sheriff's department and keep the citizens of Montgomery County safe. EmergeNYC Montgomery County free update coming soon. Visit our brand new website for more info: https://www.emergenyc.net/

EmergeNYC Pre-Alpha available on Steam Early Access Now
https://store.steampowered.com/app/461430?snr=2_100300_300__100301

Official Facebook Page: https://www.facebook.com/EmergenycGame/
Official EmergeNYC Community: https://www.facebook.com/groups/445211119186559/
Official Youtube Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/rafaelmfernandezable
Official Twitter: https://twitter.com/FSGEmergeNYC
